{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "assigame-api-collection",
    "name": "Assigamé API",
    "description": "Collection Postman pour tester l'API REST Assigamé (Spring Boot + JWT).\n\n## Démarrage rapide\n1. Importer `Assigame-Local.postman_environment.json`\n2. Démarrer le backend : `mvnw spring-boot:run` (port 8080)\n3. **02 — Public** → Liste catégories (définit `categoryId`)\n4. **01 — Auth** → Login Vendeur ou Login Admin\n5. **03 — Vendeur** → Mes produits (prépare `productId`) avant Modifier/Supprimer\n\nVariables auto : `token`, `productId`, `categoryId`, `sellerUserId`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01 — Auth",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login Vendeur",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Connexion réussie (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.test('Token JWT présent', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.token).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "    });",
                  "    pm.environment.set('token', json.token);",
                  "    if (json.user && json.user.id_utilisateur) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set('sellerUserId', String(json.user.id_utilisateur));",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{sellerEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{sellerPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Admin",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Connexion réussie (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('token', json.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Profil connecté (GET /auth/me)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Profil accessible (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Email utilisateur présent', function () {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.mail_utilisateur).to.be.a('string');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "02 — Public (sans token)",
      "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Santé API",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('API en ligne (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('status UP', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().status).to.eql('UP');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Liste produits",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Liste produits (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Réponse est un tableau', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});",
                  "if (pm.response.json().length > 0) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('productId', String(pm.response.json()[0].id_produit));",
                  "    console.log('productId (public) =', pm.response.json()[0].id_produit, '— pour vendeur, utilisez 03 > Mes produits');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/produit/list"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Détail produit par ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/produit/{{productId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Image produit",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Image ou 404 si absente', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect([200, 404]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/produit/{{productId}}/image"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Liste catégories",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Liste catégories (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "const categories = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (categories.length > 0) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('categoryId', String(categories[0].idcategorie_produit));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/categorieproduit/list"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Détail catégorie par ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/categorieproduit/{{categoryId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Image catégorie",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Image ou 404 si absente', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect([200, 404]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/categorieproduit/{{categoryId}}/image"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Inscription vendeur (public)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.request.headers.remove('Authorization');",
                  "pm.environment.set('registerEmail', 'test.postman.' + Date.now() + '@assigame.tg');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Inscription vendeur (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nom_utilisateur\": \"Test\",\n  \"prenom_utilisateur\": \"Postman\",\n  \"sexe_utilisateur\": \"M\",\n  \"telephone_utilisateur\": \"+22890111222\",\n  \"mail_utilisateur\": \"{{registerEmail}}\",\n  \"password_utilisateur\": \"test12345\",\n  \"residence_utilisateur\": \"Lomé\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/users/add"
          },
          "description": "Inscription publique — le rôle vendeur est forcé côté serveur (pas de `type_utilisateur` dans le body)."
        },
        {
          "name": "Liste types utilisateur",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/typeutilisateur/list"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "03 — Vendeur (SELLER)",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Mes produits (prépare productId)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Liste produits (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "const products = pm.response.json();",
                  "const sellerId = Number(pm.environment.get('sellerUserId'));",
                  "const mine = products.filter(function (p) {",
                  "    return p.utilisateur && Number(p.utilisateur.id_utilisateur) === sellerId;",
                  "});",
                  "if (mine.length > 0) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('productId', String(mine[0].id_produit));",
                  "    pm.test('productId défini pour le vendeur connecté', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(mine[0].id_produit).to.exist;",
                  "    });",
                  "} else {",
                  "    pm.test('Aucun produit vendeur — créez-en un avant Modifier/Supprimer', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect.fail('Exécutez Créer produit (image URL) puis réessayez');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/produit/list"
          },
          "description": "À exécuter après **Login Vendeur**. Met à jour `{{productId}}` avec un produit appartenant au vendeur connecté."
        },
        {
          "name": "Créer produit (image URL)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Produit créé (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('productId', String(json.id_produit));",
                  "    pm.test('has_image ou id présent', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.id_produit).to.exist;",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "nom_produit", "value": "Produit test Postman", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "statut", "value": "actif", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "description", "value": "Créé via Postman", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "prix", "value": "35000", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "id_categorie", "value": "{{categoryId}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "id_utilisateur", "value": "{{sellerUserId}}", "type": "text" },
                {
                  "key": "image_url",
                  "value": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523275335684-37898b6baf30?w=800",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/produit/add"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Créer produit (fichier image)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "nom_produit", "value": "Produit avec fichier", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "statut", "value": "actif", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "description", "value": "Upload fichier Postman", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "prix", "value": "42000", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "id_categorie", "value": "{{categoryId}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "id_utilisateur", "value": "{{sellerUserId}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "file", "type": "file", "src": [] }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/produit/add"
          },
          "description": "Dans l'onglet Body → form-data, cliquez sur **file** et sélectionnez une image (.jpg, .png)."
        },
        {
          "name": "Modifier produit",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 404) {",
                  "    console.log('404 : produit {{productId}} introuvable ou supprimé.');",
                  "    console.log('→ Exécutez Login Vendeur, puis Mes produits (prépare productId).');",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('Produit modifié (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "nom_produit", "value": "Produit modifié Postman", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "prix", "value": "38000", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "statut", "value": "actif", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/produit/update/{{productId}}"
          },
          "description": "Ordre : **Login Vendeur** → **Mes produits (prépare productId)** → cette requête.\n\n404 = `{{productId}}` n'existe pas dans votre base locale."
        },
        {
          "name": "Changer image (upload-image)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Image mise à jour (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "image_url",
                  "value": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505740420928-5e560c06d30e?w=800",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/produit/{{productId}}/upload-image"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Supprimer produit",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Produit supprimé (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/produit/delete/{{productId}}"
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "Exécutez d'abord **01 — Auth → Login Vendeur** pour obtenir un token SELLER."
    },
    {
      "name": "04 — Admin",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Liste utilisateurs",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Accès admin (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/users/list"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Ajouter catégorie",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Catégorie créée (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('categoryId', String(json.idcategorie_produit));",
                  "    pm.environment.set('testCategoryId', String(json.idcategorie_produit));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nom_categorieproduit\": \"Test Postman\",\n  \"description\": \"Catégorie créée via Postman\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/categorieproduit/add"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Modifier catégorie",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nom_categorieproduit\": \"Test Postman modifié\",\n  \"description\": \"Mise à jour\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/categorieproduit/update/{{testCategoryId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Image catégorie (upload)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "image_url",
                  "value": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1445205170230-053b83016050?w=800",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/categorieproduit/{{testCategoryId}}/upload-image"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Supprimer catégorie",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Catégorie supprimée (200)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/categorieproduit/delete/{{testCategoryId}}"
          },
          "description": "Exécutez **Ajouter catégorie** avant — supprime la catégorie de test (`testCategoryId`), pas une catégorie seed."
        }
      ],
      "description": "Exécutez d'abord **01 — Auth → Login Admin** pour obtenir un token ADMIN."
    },
    {
      "name": "05 — Erreurs (tests négatifs)",
      "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login — mauvais mot de passe (401)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Refus attendu (401)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(401);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"kodjo@assigame.tg\",\n  \"password\": \"mauvais\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /auth/me sans token (401)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Non authentifié (401)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(401);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Vendeur → liste users (403)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const baseUrl = pm.environment.get('baseUrl');",
                  "pm.sendRequest({",
                  "    url: baseUrl + '/auth/login',",
                  "    method: 'POST',",
                  "    header: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },",
                  "    body: {",
                  "        mode: 'raw',",
                  "        raw: JSON.stringify({",
                  "            email: pm.environment.get('sellerEmail'),",
                  "            password: pm.environment.get('sellerPassword')",
                  "        })",
                  "    }",
                  "}, function (err, res) {",
                  "    if (err || res.code !== 200) {",
                  "        console.warn('Login vendeur prerequest échoué — vérifiez sellerEmail/sellerPassword');",
                  "        return;",
                  "    }",
                  "    const token = res.json().token;",
                  "    pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'Authorization', value: 'Bearer ' + token });",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Accès refusé vendeur (403)', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(403);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/users/list"
          },
          "description": "Connectez-vous en **vendeur** puis lancez cette requête : seul ADMIN peut lister les users."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
